<title>AUSTRALIA: Crown taps ANZ, Bank of America.</title>
<headline>Crown taps ANZ, Bank of America.</headline>
<dateline>MELBOURNE 1997-07-30</dateline>
<text>
<p>Australian casino company Crown Ltd on Wednesday said it had established new debt facilities with the Australia and New Zealand Banking Group and Bank of America.</p>
<p>The new facilities have been established, and are being drawn down, as part of a recently announced refinancing of Crown's secured borrowings, the company said.</p>
